{"skill_name": "test-fix-loop", "description": "Automatically find why tests fail and fix the right code.", "rationale": "This fix-and-rerun cycle appeared 4 times across sessions.\n- Automating it saves many rounds of back-and-forth\n- The steps are consistent enough to reuse", "addressed_patterns": ["Fixing Failing Tests Takes Many Rounds"], "confidence": 0.82}

